title: Kirill Marushchak
text:
Kirill Valeryevich Marushchak (; born 16 May 1986) is a Russian former professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Volgar-Gazprom%20Astrakhan">FC Volgar-Gazprom Astrakhan</a> on 27 March 2010 in a game against <a href="FC%20KAMAZ%20Naberezhnye%20Chelny">FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny</a>.
